label: Functional Failure
description: An ISO: Activity that is represented in a OMPD: Failure Mode Observation and hasParticipant some OMPD: Maintainable Item

label: Failure Event
description: An ISO:Event that resuts in a OMPD: Functional Failure

label: Failure Mode Observation
description: An ISO:Information object that denotes a OMPD:functional failure

label: Corrective Maintenance Task
description: A OMPD:maintenance task that addresses a OMPD:functional failure
